---
title: HelloHero: Beef Meatballs & Cheesy Mash with Caramelised Bacon-Onion Sauce & Sautéed Veggies
description: Easy cheesy potato mash coming right up! Do we hear a call for beef meatballs drizzled in a sweet caramelised onion sauce,  we’re on it. For the finishing fresh touch, sautéed veggies. Plate up and bon appétit.

"We’ve replaced the pea pods in this recipe with green beans due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!"
